description:
Discover the exceptional value and capabilities of the 2021 Ford Ranger XL. This versatile pickup offers a winning combination of power, technology, and style, making it the ideal choice for those seeking a rugged and reliable companion on the road.

Boasting a bold and eye-catching exterior, the Ranger XL stands out with its:
Chrome Front & Rear Bumpers
Fog Lamps
Body-Color Wheel-Lip Molding
Class IV Trailer Hitch Receiver

Under the hood, the Ranger XL's EcoBoost 2.3L I4 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine delivers impressive performance, while the 10-speed automatic transmission ensures smooth and efficient power delivery. With a fuel-efficient rating of 21 city/26 highway MPG, this truck offers the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

The Ranger XL's impressive list of features includes:
SYNC, enhanced voice recognition communications and entertainment system
911 Assist
Remote Key Fob with Tailgate Lock
Electronic-Locking Rear Differential
Manual-Sliding Rear-Window with Privacy Glass and Defrost

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or embarking on outdoor adventures, the Ranger XL is equipped to handle it all. The Trailer Tow Package and XL Chrome Appearance Package further enhance the truck's capabilities and style, making it a true workhorse with a touch of sophistication.

Comfort and convenience are also prioritized in the Ranger XL, with amenities such as air conditioning, power windows, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. The spacious interior and thoughtful design ensure a pleasant driving experience, no matter the journey.

Experience the uncompromising performance, rugged capabilities, and refined features of the 2021 Ford Ranger XL. This exceptional pickup is ready to take on your toughest challenges and elevate your driving experience to new heights.

The listed online price reflects a $1,000 finance incentive and a $1,000 qualifying retail trade-in incentive; absence of either or both incentives will result in an increase of up to $2,000 to the final sale price.

description: Selling my 2014 Chevy Volt with approximately 93k miles. This has been a reliable, efficient daily driver and has treated me very well. I'm only selling because I no longer need the car. Clean title in hand. Located in Buda, TX. This would make an excellent commuter car, first car, or efficient second vehicle. Excellent efficiency: Drives about 35 miles full electric before switching to the gas engine, which gets ~40 MPG. Perfect for short commutes and city driving. Plug-in hybrid convenience: Charge at home up to 12 Amps. Smooth, comfortable ride with a quiet interior. Drives strong  engine, transmission, and battery all operate normally. Battery system is still healthy and efficient. OEM Chevy charging cable included  ready to plug in and use. Dealer-performed maintenance with records available, showing the car has been properly cared for. Well-maintained and dependable  not a neglected vehicle. Condition (Priced Accordingly & Transparently): Exterior: Some clear-coat fading in a couple areas (cosmetic only). Mechanical: Small oil leak from the oil pan (minor, disclosed, and reflected in price). Interior: Clean, functional, and well cared for. Tires & brakes: In good condition. This Volt is a solid, economical car that still has plenty of life left and extremely low operating costs compared to traditional gas vehicles. Price: $7,000 OBO Serious buyers only, please. Happy to answer questions or show maintenance records. Thanks, John

Elevate Your Driving Experience with the 2021 Hyundai Elantra Limited

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in the 2021 Hyundai Elantra Limited. This exceptional vehicle is designed to elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures alike, offering a remarkable combination of features that cater to your every need.

Navigation System
Radio: AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Display Audio
Front dual zone A/C
Power driver seat
Low tire pressure warning
Power moonroof
Auto High-beam Headlights
Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
Heated Front Bucket Seats
Leather-Trimmed Seats
17 x 7.0J Alloy Wheels

Slip behind the wheel of this Elantra Limited and experience the epitome of modern automotive engineering. The 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 31 MPG in the city and 41 MPG on the highway.

The exterior of the Elantra Limited exudes a sophisticated and sleek appearance, with its Gray finish accentuating the vehicle's bold, sculpted lines. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a cabin that seamlessly blends premium materials and advanced technology, creating an environment that is both visually appealing and highly functional.

Convenience and connectivity are at the forefront of the Elantra Limited's design. The intuitive infotainment system, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, allows you to stay connected and entertained on the go. The dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone on board enjoys their ideal temperature, while the power driver's seat and heated front buckets provide exceptional comfort.

Safety is also a top priority in the Elantra Limited. With features like the Rear Camera, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist, you can drive with confidence, knowing that advanced safety technologies are working to protect you and your passengers.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a road trip, or simply enjoying the daily drive, the 2021 Hyundai Elantra Limited is the perfect companion. Experience the exceptional blend of style, technology, and performance that this remarkable vehicle has to offer. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the joy of driving the Elantra Limited.

description:
The 2021 Chevrolet Bolt EV 2LT establishes itself as a leader in automotive connectivity with a vibrant touchscreen infotainment system, supporting both Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. Wireless connectivity, SiriusXM radio, and Bluetooth enable effortless streaming and app access, transforming every drive into a digital experience.

Tech-centric drivers seeking a fully connected ride will appreciate how this Bolt EV 2LT empowers multitasking on the go. Its Chevrolet MyLink system, voice controls, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls cater to those who want hands-free access to navigation, messages, and favorite apps. The Comfort & Convenience Package further appeals to users prioritizing smart cabin ergonomics.

Every aspect of the Bolt EV s performance is digitally optimized. The all-electric powertrain delivers instant torque via electronic throttle response, while regenerative braking recaptures energy for extended range. Drive modes allow tailored performance, and the Bolt s robust 127 city/108 highway MPGe efficiency is achieved through advanced power management systems supporting eco-conscious driving.

Active safety in the Bolt EV 2LT leverages a suite of electronic systems: sensors monitor surroundings for threats while stability and traction control enhance handling in real time. The Driver Confidence Package adds smart features like lane-keeping assistance and a rear camera, using digital processing to warn drivers and assist in accident prevention, prioritizing tech-enabled peace of mind.

Included features extend far beyond the essentials, with the Chevrolet Infotainment System AM/FM Stereo, 6-speaker premium audio, automatic climate control, and OnStar connected services. The Comfort & Convenience Package delivers heated mirrors and easy seat adjustments, while the Driver Confidence Package introduces advanced driver aids, fusing comfort with high-tech utility.

Compared to the Nissan Leaf and Hyundai Kona Electric, the Bolt EV 2LT stands out with its larger infotainment ecosystem, quicker smartphone pairing, and a more comprehensive app suite. Over-the-air update capability means its digital features improve over time, ensuring lasting relevance for those who value staying ahead in connectivity.

Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto are fully integrated, eliminating the need for cables. The Driver Confidence Package includes lane-keeping and rear camera tech. The infotainment system s screen and responsiveness rival competitors, and Chevy s MyLink app enables remote start, lock, and vehicle status directly from your smartphone for ultimate convenience.

Experience the 2021 Chevrolet Bolt EV 2LT s advanced connectivity at Bayway Chevrolet. Schedule a test drive or inquire about features by calling 346-300-4427 or visiting 5719 Broadway St, Pearland, TX, 77581. Stay connected and drive into the digital future with innovative technology designed for today s lifestyle.
